  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the safety and efficacy of letrozole monotherapy at a dose of 2.5 mg/day in
      postmenopausal patients with breast cancer, and to determine the blood concentrations of
      letrozole and hormones.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
